<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kauflewte an ew
                                <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> freyheiten
                        in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und herscheften. Also
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dienst willen den
                            <expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>kawflewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Österrich fürderlich und beholffen sein wöllet
                        und ew darynne gütlichen und <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweisen,
                        als etc. Und das etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Lucie ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
